---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Impressum & Privacy Policy // Yanis Amani"
  description="Legal notice and privacy policy for Yanis Amani's portfolio.">
  <section data-lang="en">
    <section class="legal-page" data-animate>
      <div class="container">
        <a href="/" class="legal-back">Back to Home ↗</a>

        <div class="legal-header">
          <span class="legal-tag">Legal Info</span>
          <div class="accent-rule"></div>
          <h1 class="legal-title">
            IMPRESSUM &<br/>
            <span class="legal-accent">PRIVACY POLICY</span>
          </h1>
          <p class="legal-date">Last Update // July 2026</p>
        </div>

        <div class="legal-sections">
          <div class="legal-section" data-animate>
            <div class="legal-section-grid">
              <div>
                <h2 class="legal-h2">YANIS AMANI</h2>
                <p class="legal-p">Computer Science Student @ HE-Arc<br/>Neuchâtel, Switzerland</p>
              </div>
              <div>
                <span class="legal-field-label">Contact Direct</span>
                <a href="mailto:yanis.amani@icloud.com" class="legal-email">yanis.amani@icloud.com</a>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="legal-section" data-animate>
            <div class="legal-section-content">
              <h2 class="legal-h2">PRIVACY FIRST POLICY</h2>
              <p class="legal-p">This website is built with privacy in mind. No tracking cookies are used, and no third-party analytics are active.</p>
              <div class="legal-highlight">
                <h3 class="legal-highlight-label">Your Rights</h3>
                <p class="legal-p">You have the right to access, change, or delete any personal information sent through official channels.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="legal-section" data-animate>
            <div>
              <h2 class="legal-h2">INFOMANIAK NETWORK SA</h2>
              <p class="legal-p">Rue Eugène-Marziano 25, 1227 Les Acacias, Switzerland</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="legal-footer">
          <a href="/" class="btn-primary">Back to Home</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </section>

  <section data-lang="fr">
    <section class="legal-page" data-animate>
      <div class="container">
        <a href="/" class="legal-back">Retour à l'accueil ↗</a>

        <div class="legal-header">
          <span class="legal-tag">Infos Légales</span>
          <div class="accent-rule"></div>
          <h1 class="legal-title">
            MENTIONS LÉGALES &<br/>
            <span class="legal-accent">CONFIDENTIALITÉ</span>
          </h1>
          <p class="legal-date">Dernière MAJ // Juillet 2026</p>
        </div>

        <div class="legal-sections">
          <div class="legal-section" data-animate>
            <div class="legal-section-grid">
              <div>
                <h2 class="legal-h2">YANIS AMANI</h2>
                <p class="legal-p">Étudiant en Informatique @ HE-Arc<br/>Neuchâtel, Suisse</p>
              </div>
              <div>
                <span class="legal-field-label">Contact Direct</span>
                <a href="mailto:yanis.amani@icloud.com" class="legal-email">yanis.amani@icloud.com</a>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="legal-section" data-animate>
            <div class="legal-section-content">
              <h2 class="legal-h2">POLITIQUE CONFIDENTIALITÉ</h2>
              <p class="legal-p">Ce site est conçu dans le respect de votre vie privée. Aucun cookie de traçage n'est utilisé, et aucun script d'analyse tiers n'est actif.</p>
              <div class="legal-highlight">
                <h3 class="legal-highlight-label">Vos Droits</h3>
                <p class="legal-p">Vous disposez d'un droit d'accès, de modification et d'effacement de toute information transmise via les canaux officiels.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="legal-section" data-animate>
            <div>
              <h2 class="legal-h2">INFOMANIAK NETWORK SA</h2>
              <p class="legal-p">Rue Eugène-Marziano 25, 1227 Les Acacias, Suisse</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="legal-footer">
          <a href="/" class="btn-primary">Retour à l'accueil</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .legal-page { padding: 6rem 1.5rem; }
  .legal-back {
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    text-decoration: none;
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
    transition: color 0.2s;
  }
  .legal-back:hover { color: var(--text); }

  .legal-header { margin-bottom: 5rem; }
  .legal-tag {
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    color: var(--accent);
    font-weight: 500;
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
    display: block;
  }
  .legal-header .accent-rule { margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
  .legal-title {
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3.5rem);
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    line-height: 0.95;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  .legal-accent { font-style: italic; color: var(--accent); }
  .legal-date { font-size: 0.75rem; color: var(--text-dim); text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.1em; }

  .legal-sections { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 4rem; }

  .legal-section {
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 2rem;
    background: var(--surface);
  }
  @media (min-width: 768px) { .legal-section { padding: 3rem; } }

  .legal-section-label {
    font-size: 0.6rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    color: var(--accent);
    font-weight: 500;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    display: block;
  }

  .legal-section-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 2.5rem;
  }
  @media (min-width: 768px) { .legal-section-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; } }

  .legal-h2 {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .legal-p {
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .legal-field-label {
    font-size: 0.6rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    color: var(--text-dim);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    display: block;
  }

  .legal-email {
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--accent);
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: color 0.2s;
    word-break: break-all;
  }
  .legal-email:hover { color: var(--accent-hover); }

  .legal-section-content { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 1.5rem; }

  .legal-highlight {
    padding: 1.5rem;
    border: 1px solid rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.2);
    background: var(--accent-light);
    border-radius: 8px;
  }
  .legal-highlight-label {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    color: var(--accent);
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .legal-footer {
    margin-top: 6rem;
    padding-top: 3rem;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
    text-align: center;
  }
</style>
